<div class="container about-container my-5">
  <div class="row align-items-center">
    <!-- LEFT: TEXT -->
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h1 class="mb-4 fw-bold text-center my-5">About</h1>

      <p class="mb-4">
        Dropby is a curated vintage destination founded by Helene Gaspar in Paris.
        Each month, we release handpicked luxury vintage pieces through our Sunday drops
        (announced on Instagram stories).
      </p>

      <p class="mb-4">
        Dropby is a carefully curated vintage boutique and archive for women.
        We offer luxury vintage from the 1970s to the 2000s,
        bringing it to our customers at a reasonable price point.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-4">
        The excitement of Dropby comes with the drop itself—our monthly Sunday sale,
        where unique pieces are released and claimed in real time.
      </p>

      <a href="https://instagram.com/YOUR_INSTAGRAM_HANDLE"
        target="_blank"
        class="btn btn-dark d-inline-flex align-items-center mt-3">
